### Which @angular/* package(s) are the source of the bug?

core

### Is this a regression?

No

### Description

Input:
```
<ng-template [ngIf]="viewModel$ | async" let-vm>
  {{vm | json}}
</ng-template>
```

Output:
```
@if (viewModel$ | async) {
  {{vm | json}}
}
```

Expected:
```
@if (viewModel$ | async; as vm) {
  {{vm | json}}
}

```

